                            </div>
                            <p class="validationContainer" id="ValidateClaimDetails3"></p>

                        </section>

                    </section>


                    <section class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">


                        <label class="label cgmodalLabel">1. HAVE YOU OR ANY PERSON OR ENTITY TO BE COVERED UNDER THE PROPOSED INSURANCE, OR ANY PERSON WHO MAY BENEFIT FROM THE PROPOSED INSURANCE:</label>

                        <section class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-md-9 col-lg-9">
                            <label class="label required">
                                a) Ever been charged with, convicted of, or have a pending prosecution for any criminal or statutory offence? The answer to this question may be subjected to the provisions of the Criminal Records(Clean Slate)Act.
                            </label>
                        </section>
                        <section class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-3 col-md-3 col-lg-3">
